column5: Does anyone know how the bridge in Sioux Narrows is doing? What are the plans for it? Is the highway going to be closed at all?
I just went through there two weeks ago........it's down to one lane and they are working on it. I don't think it will be completely closed.
They will not be closing it this summer, they are looking at a study period to see what can be done to fix it.In the mean time it will be down to one lane, controlled by lights.
